{"tid":1440431,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"而家警方既做法擺明分化和理非同埋勇武人士","createTime":"2019-08-10T12:16:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T04:58:35.000Z","uid":227981,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"27c91790084dbdd96e93af43b4de6225160cf984","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"有冇人有一個有效既方法可以俾和理非表達自己既訴求？ 而家警方只有反對通知書，咁好明顯想隔絕勇武派出黎。<br />\n而家警權真係唔公平！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人知道有咩方法可以鏟爆呢個「一哥」狗既所作所為，連香港既集會自由都由自己放充棄。<br />\n<br />\n我地呢想繼續為呢個運動發聲既，被滅聲了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n釋放盧偉聰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b756b1d3805cb139862e610f27e8a7a3d51f3df9","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:17:13.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"8290d27975e2658ae6ab8975e1c04c3b2ff93023","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:18:03.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n釋放盧偉聰"},{"pid":"9cce1069a56f9492dab9c5d58012fa2ebb670d3b","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n釋放盧偉聰"},{"pid":"9782c9c667d6f5bc4c08c854a7147a3f5e87c00c","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:19:08.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n釋放盧偉聰"},{"pid":"c19dffd4b651eb58698642afb59ccabcbadbc59d","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:19:32.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<br />\n釋放盧偉聰"},{"pid":"63eaff6ee0de4eb4bc5dfcb018604e6ecae1525f","tid":1440431,"uid":227981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit